overwritten during a future update.</p>

<p><img alt="Blog Photo" src="https://grovetech.co/assets/img/blog/2020/20200803Ho/Creative-Cloud-versions.png" class="img-fluid rounded m-2" width="700" /></p>

<p>You can ensure that you donâ€™t lose access to older versions during
updates by disabling a Creative Cloud setting that automatically removes
previous versions of apps when you update. In the Creative Cloud app,
